collectible.name: RARE PEPE GOLD CHAIN
collectible.author: 0x5fae9d4b591f213b3ba75287f2cfac0883d17f7a
collectible.description:
This is an exclusive gold pendant for accessing the VIP portal at Rare Villa in Cryptovoxels - 11 The Embarcadero
in San Francisco. This pendant is given to any holders of the Honey Badger Async Music plaques. You must have the token in your metamask or similar wallet to receive on on October 16, 2021. 

Created by Luifex
